history.content:
Online Faculty Advising for CS-Intended Students 4/13
Tuesday 4/13/21 @ 1-2PM PST

Zoom link: https://berkeley.zoom.us/j/92099658754

Are you looking for help from a faculty perspective to choose your Fall 2021 schedule? Or for advice regarding industry or research? This semester Professor Gireeja Ranade will be hosting an online Faculty Advising session for CS-intended students.
No registration is required, open to all. Freshmen are particularly welcome. Join us!
